author: ate
msg: Further refining the pages deploy/undeploy targets which caused failures when running with Maven 2.2.1/JDK 1.6
Note: with Maven 2.2.1 it seems plugin execution order is reversed (top-down) from Maven 2.0.10 (down-up).
Fixed by using only a single execution and a separate jetspeed:mvn target (dependency) to delete target pages folder first
